title: USGS M2.5+ Earthquakes feed
name: USGS M2.5+ Earthquakes feed
description:
Data file containing the source network (Src), ID (Eqid), version, date, location, magnitude, depth (km) and number of reporting stations (NST) for each earthquake. Note: files are not inclusive (the past day file does not include past hour events, for example).

This data was made available through the USGS and included a listing of reported earthquake activity with a magnitude of 1 and greater. Included in this dataset are the locations of the quakes that hit the Haiti region on 1/12/10.
